Explain about thread synchronization(inter-thread communication).


nter-thread communication or Co-operation is all about 
allowing synchronized threads to communicate with each other.

Cooperation (Inter-thread communication) is a mechanism 
in which a thread is paused running in its critical section and 
another thread is allowed to enter (or lock) in the same critical
 section to be executed.It is implemented by following methods of 
 Object class:

wait()
notify()
notifyAll()